        "text_k369xK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": false,
            "text": "<p>We collect the following types of information:</p><h2>1.1 Personal Information (Provided by You)</h2><p>When you register as a member, place an order, or contact us, you may provide:</p><ul><li>Full name<br/></li><li>Email address<br/></li><li>Phone number<br/></li><li>Password and login information<br/></li><li>Billing and shipping address<br/></li><li>Payment details (processed securely by payment gateways)<br/></li><li>Team, organization, or company details (if provided)<br/></li></ul><h2>1.2 Automatically Collected Information</h2><p>When you use our website, we may collect:</p><ul><li>IP address<br/></li><li>Browser type<br/></li><li>Device information<br/></li><li>Cookies and tracking data<br/></li><li>Pages visited and time spent<br/></li><li>Referral URLs<br/></li></ul><h2>1.3 Membership-Specific Information</h2><p>Because we offer networking and membership functionality, we may collect:</p><ul><li>Profile information (bio, profile photo, location, business details)<br/></li><li>Players, teams, companies or groups you join or follow<br/></li><li>Content you post, upload, or share<br/></li><li>Interactions with other members<br/></li><li>Preferences and activity logs inside the membership area</li></ul>"
